{"data":[{"name":"68:1","price":"ヌーン¹。筆と、それと彼らが書き記すもの²にかけて（誓う）。³","arabic":"نٓۚ وَٱلۡقَلَمِ وَمَا يَسۡطُرُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5272,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この文字については、頻出名・用語解説の「クルアーンの冒頭に現れる文字群*」を参照。 ２　天使*や人間が「書き記す」善いこと、利益、知識などのことを指す（ムヤッサル５６４頁参照）。 ３　アッラー*の「誓い」については、整列者章１の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"noon wal-qalami wamā yasṭurūna ","translations":["Nun","By the pen","and what","they write","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["noon","wal-qalami","wamā","yasṭurūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,4210],[2,4210,5190],[3,5190,5880],[4,5880,7010],[5,7010,9415]]}},{"name":"68:2","price":"（使徒*よ、）あなたは、あなたの主*の恩恵¹ゆえ、憑かれた者²などではない。","arabic":"مَآ أَنتَ بِنِعۡمَةِ رَبِّكَ بِمَجۡنُونٖ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5273,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この「恩恵」とは、預言者*性のことであるとされる（前掲書、同頁参照）。 ２　「憑かれた者」については、アル＝ヒジュル章６の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"mā anta biniʿ'mati rabbika bimajnūnin ","translations":["Not","you (are)","by (the) Grace","(of) your Lord","a madman","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","anta","biniʿ'mati","rabbika","bimajnūnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2210],[2,2210,3460],[3,3460,4530],[4,4530,5270],[5,5270,8295]]}},{"name":"68:3","price":"あなたにこそは、まさしく尽きることのない¹褒美がある。","arabic":"وَإِنَّ لَكَ لَأَجۡرًا غَيۡرَ مَمۡنُونٖ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5274,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　「尽きることのない」については、詳細にされた章８の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-inna laka la-ajran ghayra mamnūnin ","translations":["And indeed","for you","surely (is) a reward","without","end","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-inna","laka","la-ajran","ghayra","mamnūnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1570],[2,1570,2020],[3,2020,2990],[4,2990,3620],[5,3620,6545]]}},{"name":"68:4","price":"また本当に（使徒*よ）、あなたこそは、この上ない（よき）品性を備えている。","arabic":"وَإِنَّكَ لَعَلَىٰ خُلُقٍ عَظِيمٖ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5275,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-innaka laʿalā khuluqin ʿaẓīmin ","translations":["And indeed, you","surely (are)","(of) a moral character","great","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-innaka","laʿalā","khuluqin","ʿaẓīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1750],[2,1750,2530],[3,2530,3340],[4,3340,6435]]}},{"name":"68:5","price":"ならば、あなたは目にし、彼ら（不信仰者*たち）も目にするであろう、","arabic":"فَسَتُبۡصِرُ وَيُبۡصِرُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5276,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fasatub'ṣiru wayub'ṣirūna ","translations":["So you will see","and they will see","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fasatub'ṣiru","wayub'ṣirūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1250],[2,1250,4185]]}},{"name":"68:6","price":"あなた方のいずれが、試練にかけられた者¹かを。","arabic":"بِأَييِّكُمُ ٱلۡمَفۡتُونُ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5277,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　つまり、「憑（つ）かれた 者」。あるいは、「真理から迷うという試練にかけられた者」（イブン・カスィール８：１９０参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"bi-ayyikumu al-maftūnu ","translations":["Which of you","(is) the afflicted one","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["bi-ayyikumu","al-maftūnu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1150],[2,1150,4485]]}},{"name":"68:7","price":"本当にあなたの主*こそは、誰がかれの道（イスラーム*）から迷った者かを最もよくご存知であり、（正しい教えに）導かれた者たちを、最もよくご存知であられるのだ。","arabic":"إِنَّ رَبَّكَ هُوَ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَن ضَلَّ عَن سَبِيلِهِۦ وَهُوَ أَعۡلَمُ بِٱلۡمُهۡتَدِينَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5278,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna rabbaka huwa aʿlamu biman ḍalla ʿan sabīlihi wahuwa aʿlamu bil-muh'tadīna ","translations":["Indeed","your Lord","He","(is) most knowing","of (he) who","has strayed","from","His way","and He","(is) most knowing","of the guided ones","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","rabbaka","huwa","aʿlamu","biman","ḍalla","ʿan","sabīlihi","wahuwa","aʿlamu","bil-muh'tadīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1420],[2,1420,2220],[3,2220,2550],[4,2550,3400],[5,3400,4690],[6,4690,5260],[7,5260,5690],[8,5690,7610],[9,7610,8230],[10,8230,9100],[11,9100,12435]]}},{"name":"68:8","price":"ならば（使徒*よ）、（アッラー*の御徴と使徒を）噓呼ばわりする者たちに従うのではない。","arabic":"فَلَا تُطِعِ ٱلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5279,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"falā tuṭiʿi al-mukadhibīna ","translations":["So (do) not","obey","the deniers","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["falā","tuṭiʿi","al-mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,600],[2,600,1030],[3,1030,4615]]}},{"name":"68:9","price":"彼らは、あなたが（彼らの宗教に）おもねれば、彼らもおもねることを欲している。¹","arabic":"وَدُّواْ لَوۡ تُدۡهِنُ فَيُدۡهِنُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5280,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　夜の旅章７４－７５も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waddū law tud'hinu fayud'hinūna ","translations":["They wish","that","you should compromise","so they would compromise","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["waddū","law","tud'hinu","fayud'hinūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,830],[2,830,1120],[3,1120,2030],[4,2030,5305]]}},{"name":"68:10","price":"また（使徒*よ）、卑しく、やたらと誓ういかなる者にも従うのではない。","arabic":"وَلَا تُطِعۡ كُلَّ حَلَّافٖ مَّهِينٍ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5281,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"walā tuṭiʿ kulla ḥallāfin mahīnin ","translations":["And (do) not","obey","every","habitual swearer","worthless","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","tuṭiʿ","kulla","ḥallāfin","mahīnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,1180],[3,1180,1820],[4,1820,3040],[5,3040,6585]]}},{"name":"68:11","price":"中傷ばかりして¹、悪い噂を吹いて回る²（者に）。","arabic":"هَمَّازٖ مَّشَّآءِۭ بِنَمِيمٖ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5282,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この「中傷」については、中傷者章１の訳注を参照。 ２　原語では「ナミーム（またはナミーマ）」で、人間関係の悪化や、敵意を憎悪を生じさせることを意図しつつ、誰かが話したことを第三者に告げること（アッ＝サアディー８７９頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"hammāzin mashāin binamīmin ","translations":["Defamer","going about","with malicious gossip","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["hammāzin","mashāin","binamīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1880],[2,1880,6350],[3,6350,9265]]}},{"name":"68:12","price":"善を阻み、（人々への侵害と非合法な物事において）度を越し、罪に溺れた（者に）。","arabic":"مَّنَّاعٖ لِّلۡخَيۡرِ مُعۡتَدٍ أَثِيمٍ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5283,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"mannāʿin lil'khayri muʿ'tadin athīmin ","translations":["A preventer","of (the) good","transgressor","sinful","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["mannāʿin","lil'khayri","muʿ'tadin","athīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1780],[2,1780,2990],[3,2990,3970],[4,3970,6875]]}},{"name":"68:13","price":"粗暴で、その上、素性が知れない（者に）。","arabic":"عُتُلِّۭ بَعۡدَ ذَٰلِكَ زَنِيمٍ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5284,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿutullin baʿda dhālika zanīmin ","translations":["Cruel","after","(all) that","utterly useless","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿutullin","baʿda","dhālika","zanīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1380],[2,1380,2390],[3,2390,3190],[4,3190,6935]]}},{"name":"68:14","price":"財産と子供を有する者だったがゆえに（、彼は真理を受け入れることに対し、高慢になったのだ）。","arabic":"أَن كَانَ ذَا مَالٖ وَبَنِينَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5285,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"an kāna dhā mālin wabanīna ","translations":["Because","(he) is","a possessor","(of) wealth","and children","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["an","kāna","dhā","mālin","wabanīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1390],[2,1390,2060],[3,2060,2450],[4,2450,4100],[5,4100,7615]]}},{"name":"68:15","price":"われら*の御徴（アーヤ*）が彼に読誦された時、彼は言った。「（これは）昔の人々のお伽噺だ」。¹","arabic":"إِذَا تُتۡلَىٰ عَلَيۡهِ ءَايَٰتُنَا قَالَ أَسَٰطِيرُ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5286,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　アーヤ*１０－１５は、あるシルクの徒*に関して下ったとされる。その一方でこの中には、これらの性質が当てはまる者たちに対する、ムスリム*への注意の勧告が見受けられる（ムヤッサル５６４頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā tut'lā ʿalayhi āyātunā qāla asāṭīru al-awalīna ","translations":["When","are recited","to him","Our Verses","he says","Stories","(of) the former (people)","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","tut'lā","ʿalayhi","āyātunā","qāla","asāṭīru","al-awalīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,600],[2,600,1450],[3,1450,2260],[4,2260,3710],[5,3710,4410],[6,4410,5530],[7,5530,9235]]}},{"name":"68:16","price":"われら*は彼に対し（人の目に明らかな懲罰として）、鼻の上に印をつけてやろう。¹","arabic":"سَنَسِمُهُۥ عَلَى ٱلۡخُرۡطُومِ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5287,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　このアーヤ*の解釈には「剣で鼻を打たれる（一説に、このアーヤ*で意図された者は、バドルの戦い*において剣で鼻を打たれ、死んだとされる）」「復活の日*、他人からその姿が認められるよう、鼻に印をつけられる（慈悲あまねき*お方章４１参照）」「不名誉を与えられる」といった諸説がある（アル＝クルトゥビー１８：２３６－２３７参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"sanasimuhu ʿalā al-khur'ṭūmi ","translations":["We will brand him","on","the snout","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["sanasimuhu","ʿalā","al-khur'ṭūmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,980],[2,980,1640],[3,1640,5305]]}},{"name":"68:17","price":"本当にわれら*は、彼ら（マッカ*の民）を試練にかけた。ちょうどわれら*が農園主たちを、彼らが「朝早く、それら（果実）を摘み取ってしまおう」と誓った時、試練にかけたように。¹","arabic":"إِنَّا بَلَوۡنَٰهُمۡ كَمَا بَلَوۡنَآ أَصۡحَٰبَ ٱلۡجَنَّةِ إِذۡ أَقۡسَمُواْ لَيَصۡرِمُنَّهَا مُصۡبِحِينَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5288,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　これは、イエメン地方にあった農園主の話。この農園主は正しい人物で、果実を収穫する時には、恵まれない人々にもそこから施すことを常としていた。しかし彼の死後、それを受け継いだ三人の息子たちは分け前を惜しみ、その習いに反しようとしたのだった（前掲書１８：２４０参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"innā balawnāhum kamā balawnā aṣḥāba al-janati idh aqsamū layaṣrimunnahā muṣ'biḥīna ","translations":["Indeed, We","have tried them","as","We tried","(the) companions","(of) the garden","when","they swore","to pluck its fruit","(in the) morning","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["innā","balawnāhum","kamā","balawnā","aṣḥāba","al-janati","idh","aqsamū","layaṣrimunnahā","muṣ'biḥīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1510],[2,1510,2960],[3,2960,3570],[4,3570,5700],[5,5700,6630],[6,6630,8350],[7,8350,8710],[8,8710,9650],[9,9650,12160],[10,12160,15415]]}},{"name":"68:18","price":"（「もし、アッラー*がお望みになったならば」と言って、それが実現しない可能性を）除外することもなく（、彼らはそう誓った）。¹","arabic":"وَلَا يَسۡتَثۡنُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5289,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　関連して、洞窟章２４とその訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"walā yastathnūna ","translations":["And not","making exception","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","yastathnūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,720],[2,720,4575]]}},{"name":"68:19","price":"それで彼らが（夜中）眠っている最中、あなたの主*からの包囲¹がそれ（農園）を包囲し、","arabic":"فَطَافَ عَلَيۡهَا طَآئِفٞ مِّن رَّبِّكَ وَهُمۡ نَآئِمُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5290,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この「包囲」とは、アッラー*が天からお下しになった炎のこととされる（ムヤッサル５６５頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"faṭāfa ʿalayhā ṭāifun min rabbika wahum nāimūna ","translations":["So there came","upon it","a visitation","from","your Lord","while they","were asleep","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["faṭāfa","ʿalayhā","ṭāifun","min","rabbika","wahum","nāimūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,750],[2,750,1750],[3,1750,4270],[4,4270,5040],[5,5040,6120],[6,6120,6730],[7,6730,11255]]}},{"name":"68:20","price":"それは闇夜のように（、黒焦げに）なってしまった。","arabic":"فَأَصۡبَحَتۡ كَٱلصَّرِيمِ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5291,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-aṣbaḥat kal-ṣarīmi ","translations":["So it became","as if reaped","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-aṣbaḥat","kal-ṣarīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1170],[2,1170,4325]]}},{"name":"68:21","price":"そして彼らは朝、互いに呼びかけ合った、","arabic":"فَتَنَادَوۡاْ مُصۡبِحِينَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5292,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fatanādaw muṣ'biḥīna ","translations":["And they called one another","(at) morning","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["fatanādaw","muṣ'biḥīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,4245]]}},{"name":"68:22","price":"「あなた方の作物へと、朝早く出かけよ。もしあなた方が、（それを）摘み取るのならば」と。","arabic":"أَنِ ٱغۡدُواْ عَلَىٰ حَرۡثِكُمۡ إِن كُنتُمۡ صَٰرِمِينَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5293,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ani igh'dū ʿalā ḥarthikum in kuntum ṣārimīna ","translations":["That","Go early","to","your crop","if","you would","pluck (the) fruit","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["ani","igh'dū","ʿalā","ḥarthikum","in","kuntum","ṣārimīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,390],[2,390,950],[3,950,1610],[4,1610,2630],[5,2630,3560],[6,3560,5140],[7,5140,8175]]}},{"name":"68:23","price":"それで彼らは、ひそひそ話し合いつつ出発した。","arabic":"فَٱنطَلَقُواْ وَهُمۡ يَتَخَٰفَتُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5294,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-inṭalaqū wahum yatakhāfatūna ","translations":["So they went","while they","lowered (their) voices","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-inṭalaqū","wahum","yatakhāfatūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1900],[2,1900,2420],[3,2420,6395]]}},{"name":"68:24","price":"「今日は貧者*があなた方と共に、そこ（農園）に入ることがあってはならない」と。","arabic":"أَن لَّا يَدۡخُلَنَّهَا ٱلۡيَوۡمَ عَلَيۡكُم مِّسۡكِينٞ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5295,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"an lā yadkhulannahā al-yawma ʿalaykum mis'kīnun ","translations":["That","Not","will enter it","today","upon you","any poor person","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["an","lā","yadkhulannahā","al-yawma","ʿalaykum","mis'kīnun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,300],[2,300,850],[3,850,2800],[4,2800,3630],[5,3630,4770],[6,4770,8275]]}},{"name":"68:25","price":"そして（貧者*たちに果実を）禁じようとして、（計画を実行する）力にみなぎった状態で、朝に出かけた。","arabic":"وَغَدَوۡاْ عَلَىٰ حَرۡدٖ قَٰدِرِينَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5296,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waghadaw ʿalā ḥardin qādirīna ","translations":["And they went early","with","determination","able","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["waghadaw","ʿalā","ḥardin","qādirīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,1420],[3,1420,3180],[4,3180,6845]]}},{"name":"68:26","price":"それで、それ（黒焦げになった農園）を見た時、彼らは（信じられず、こう）言った。「本当に私たちは（農園への道で）、迷子になってしまったのだ」。","arabic":"فَلَمَّا رَأَوۡهَا قَالُوٓاْ إِنَّا لَضَآلُّونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5297,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"falammā ra-awhā qālū innā laḍāllūna ","translations":["But when","they saw it","they said","Indeed, we","(are) surely lost","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["falammā","ra-awhā","qālū","innā","laḍāllūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1290],[2,1290,2290],[3,2290,4450],[4,4450,5780],[5,5780,12235]]}},{"name":"68:27","price":"（そして、それが自分たちの農園だと認めた時、彼らは言った。）「いや、私たちは（農園の恵みを）禁じられたのである」","arabic":"بَلۡ نَحۡنُ مَحۡرُومُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5298,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"bal naḥnu maḥrūmūna ","translations":["Nay","We","(are) deprived","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["bal","naḥnu","maḥrūmūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,420],[2,420,1000],[3,1000,4635]]}},{"name":"68:28","price":"彼らの内、最善の者が言った。「私はあなた方に、『さあ、称える*¹のだ』と言わなかったか？」","arabic":"قَالَ أَوۡسَطُهُمۡ أَلَمۡ أَقُل لَّكُمۡ لَوۡلَا تُسَبِّحُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5299,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　つまり、アーヤ*１８にあるように「もし、アッラー*がお望みになったら」という言葉のこと（ムヤッサル５６５頁参照）。この言葉が、彼らにとっての称えの言葉だったのだという。また、「アッラー*に称え*あれと言い、感謝すること」「お赦しを乞うこと」という説もある（アル＝バガウィー５：１３８参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"qāla awsaṭuhum alam aqul lakum lawlā tusabbiḥūna ","translations":["Said","(the) most moderate of them","Did not","I tell","you","'Why not","you glorify (Allah)?'","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["qāla","awsaṭuhum","alam","aqul","lakum","lawlā","tusabbiḥūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,660],[2,660,1720],[3,1720,2310],[4,2310,2850],[5,2850,3560],[6,3560,4320],[7,4320,7745]]}},{"name":"68:29","price":"彼らは言った。「アッラー*に称え*あれ。本当に私たちは、不正*者でした」。","arabic":"قَالُواْ سُبۡحَٰنَ رَبِّنَآ إِنَّا كُنَّا ظَٰلِمِينَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5300,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"qālū sub'ḥāna rabbinā innā kunnā ẓālimīna ","translations":["They said","Glory be","(to) our Lord","Indeed, we","[we] were","wrongdoers","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["qālū","sub'ḥāna","rabbinā","innā","kunnā","ẓālimīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,760],[2,760,1800],[3,1800,4240],[4,4240,5510],[5,5510,7080],[6,7080,10535]]}},{"name":"68:30","price":"彼らは互いに、責め合い出した。","arabic":"فَأَقۡبَلَ بَعۡضُهُمۡ عَلَىٰ بَعۡضٖ يَتَلَٰوَمُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5301,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-aqbala baʿḍuhum ʿalā baʿḍin yatalāwamūna ","translations":["Then approached","some of them","to","others","blaming each other","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-aqbala","baʿḍuhum","ʿalā","baʿḍin","yatalāwamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1100],[2,1100,2050],[3,2050,2680],[4,2680,4100],[5,4100,7715]]}},{"name":"68:31","price":"彼らは言った。「我らが災いよ！¹本当に私たちは、放埓者でした。","arabic":"قَالُواْ يَٰوَيۡلَنَآ إِنَّا كُنَّا طَٰغِينَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5302,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この表現については、食卓章３１「我が災いよ！」の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"qālū yāwaylanā innā kunnā ṭāghīna ","translations":["They said","O woe to us","Indeed, we","[we] were","transgressors","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["qālū","yāwaylanā","innā","kunnā","ṭāghīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,3930],[3,3930,5210],[4,5210,6640],[5,6640,9755]]}},{"name":"68:32","price":"我らが主*は、きっとあれ（農園）より善いものを、私たちに取り替えて下さろう。本当に私たちは、我らが主*にこそ、（お赦しとお恵みを）切望するのだから」。","arabic":"عَسَىٰ رَبُّنَآ أَن يُبۡدِلَنَا خَيۡرٗا مِّنۡهَآ إِنَّآ إِلَىٰ رَبِّنَا رَٰغِبُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5303,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿasā rabbunā an yub'dilanā khayran min'hā innā ilā rabbinā rāghibūna ","translations":["Perhaps","our Lord","[that]","will substitute for us","a better","than it","Indeed, we","to","our Lord","turn devoutly","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿasā","rabbunā","an","yub'dilanā","khayran","min'hā","innā","ilā","rabbinā","rāghibūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,640],[2,640,3320],[3,3320,3620],[4,3620,5220],[5,5220,5940],[6,5940,8880],[7,8880,10060],[8,10060,12040],[9,12040,12520],[10,12520,13550],[11,13550,16745]]}},{"name":"68:33","price":"（現世の）懲罰とは、このようなもの¹。そして来世の懲罰こそは、より偉大なのである。彼らがもし、知っていたならば。","arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ ٱلۡعَذَابُۖ وَلَعَذَابُ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةِ أَكۡبَرُۚ لَوۡ كَانُواْ يَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5304,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　それら農園主のように、アッラー*のご命令に逆らい、恵まれた恩恵に対するアッラー*への義務を果たさない者には、同様の罰が下るということ（ムヤッサル５６５頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kadhālika al-ʿadhābu walaʿadhābu al-ākhirati akbaru law kānū yaʿlamūna ","translations":["Such","(is) the punishment","And surely the punishment","(of) the Hereafter","(is) greater","if","they","know","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["kadhālika","al-ʿadhābu","walaʿadhābu","al-ākhirati","akbaru","law","kānū","yaʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1030],[2,1030,4070],[3,4070,5600],[4,5600,6850],[5,6850,8080],[6,8080,8530],[7,8530,9440],[8,9440,13745]]}},{"name":"68:34","price":"実に敬虔な*者たちには、その主*の御許に安寧の楽園がある。","arabic":"إِنَّ لِلۡمُتَّقِينَ عِندَ رَبِّهِمۡ جَنَّٰتِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5305,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna lil'muttaqīna ʿinda rabbihim jannāti al-naʿīmi ","translations":["Indeed","for the righteous","with","their Lord","(are) Gardens","(of) Delight","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","lil'muttaqīna","ʿinda","rabbihim","jannāti","al-naʿīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1170],[2,1170,2640],[3,2640,3640],[4,3640,4640],[5,4640,6180],[6,6180,9905]]}},{"name":"68:35","price":"一体われら*は服従する者（ムスリム*）たちを、（その報いにおいて、不信仰に陥った）罪悪者たちのようにするであろうか？¹","arabic":"أَفَنَجۡعَلُ ٱلۡمُسۡلِمِينَ كَٱلۡمُجۡرِمِينَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5306,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　一説に、裕福だったクライシュ族*の頭目たちは、貧しかったムスリム*たちを見て、「仮に来世があるとしても、私たちと彼らの状況は、現世における状況と同じ（で、私たちの方が豊か）か、せいぜい同じ位だろう」などと言っていた（アル＝クルトゥビー１８：２４６参照）。マルヤム*章７７も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"afanajʿalu al-mus'limīna kal-muj'rimīna ","translations":["Then will We treat","the Muslims","like the criminals","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["afanajʿalu","al-mus'limīna","kal-muj'rimīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,2520],[3,2520,6485]]}},{"name":"68:36","price":"一体、あなた方はどうしたことか？あなた方はいかに（不当な）決め方をするのか？","arabic":"مَا لَكُمۡ كَيۡفَ تَحۡكُمُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5307,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"mā lakum kayfa taḥkumūna ","translations":["What","(is) for you","How","(do) you judge","(36)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","lakum","kayfa","taḥkumūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,460],[2,460,1030],[3,1030,1640],[4,1640,4985]]}},{"name":"68:37","price":"いや、一体あなた方には啓典があり、あなた方はそれを読んでいるというのか？","arabic":"أَمۡ لَكُمۡ كِتَٰبٞ فِيهِ تَدۡرُسُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5308,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"am lakum kitābun fīhi tadrusūna ","translations":["Or","(is) for you","a book","wherein","you learn","(37)"],"transliterationArr":["am","lakum","kitābun","fīhi","tadrusūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,350],[2,350,910],[3,910,1710],[4,1710,3130],[5,3130,5985]]}},{"name":"68:38","price":"本当にその中で、あなた方は、自分たちが選ぶもの¹を手にするということを（読んで、見出したのか）？","arabic":"إِنَّ لَكُمۡ فِيهِ لَمَا تَخَيَّرُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5309,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　つまりアーヤ*３５にあるような、彼らの見解のこと（ムヤッサル５６５頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna lakum fīhi lamā takhayyarūna ","translations":["Indeed","for you","in it","what","you choose","(38)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","lakum","fīhi","lamā","takhayyarūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,1770],[3,1770,2440],[4,2440,2970],[5,2970,6165]]}},{"name":"68:39","price":"いや、一体あなた方には復活の日*まで（存続する）、われら*に対する確固とした誓約があるとでもいうのか？本当にあなた方は、自分たちが決める（思い通りの）ことを手にするという（誓約が）？","arabic":"أَمۡ لَكُمۡ أَيۡمَٰنٌ عَلَيۡنَا بَٰلِغَةٌ إِلَىٰ يَوۡمِ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ إِنَّ لَكُمۡ لَمَا تَحۡكُمُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5310,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"am lakum aymānun ʿalaynā bālighatun ilā yawmi al-qiyāmati inna lakum lamā taḥkumūna ","translations":["Or","for you","oaths","from us","reaching","to","(the) Day","(of) the Resurrection","indeed","for you","(is) what","you judge","(39)"],"transliterationArr":["am","lakum","aymānun","ʿalaynā","bālighatun","ilā","yawmi","al-qiyāmati","inna","lakum","lamā","taḥkumūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,380],[2,380,990],[3,990,2070],[4,2070,3080],[5,3080,4190],[6,4190,4820],[7,4820,5330],[8,5330,6560],[9,6560,7700],[10,7700,8230],[11,8230,8840],[12,8840,11825]]}},{"name":"68:40","price":"（使徒*よ、）彼らの内の誰がそれ¹についての保証人なのか、彼ら（シルクの徒*）に尋ねよ。","arabic":"سَلۡهُمۡ أَيُّهُم بِذَٰلِكَ زَعِيمٌ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5311,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　「それ」とは、アーヤ*３５にある、彼ら不信仰者*の思い込みのこと（ムヤッサル５６５頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"salhum ayyuhum bidhālika zaʿīmun ","translations":["Ask them","which of them","for that","(is) responsible","(40)"],"transliterationArr":["salhum","ayyuhum","bidhālika","zaʿīmun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,920],[2,920,2560],[3,2560,3500],[4,3500,6335]]}},{"name":"68:41","price":"いや、一体彼らには、（彼らがアッラー*の）同意者（とするもの）たちが（、その保証人として）あるのか？では、自分たちの同意者たちを連れて来てみるがよい。もし、彼らが本当のことを言っているというのならば。","arabic":"أَمۡ لَهُمۡ شُرَكَآءُ فَلۡيَأۡتُواْ بِشُرَكَآئِهِمۡ إِن كَانُواْ صَٰدِقِينَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5312,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"am lahum shurakāu falyatū bishurakāihim in kānū ṣādiqīna ","translations":["Or","(are) for them","partners","Then let them bring","their partners","if","they are","truthful","(41)"],"transliterationArr":["am","lahum","shurakāu","falyatū","bishurakāihim","in","kānū","ṣādiqīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,390],[2,390,930],[3,930,3510],[4,3510,4690],[5,4690,7580],[6,7580,8600],[7,8600,9370],[8,9370,12855]]}},{"name":"68:42","price":"その脛が露わにされ¹、彼ら（不信仰者*や偽信者*）がサジダ*に呼ばれ、（そうすることが）出来ない²（復活の）日*のこと（を思い起こさせよ）。","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يُكۡشَفُ عَن سَاقٖ وَيُدۡعَوۡنَ إِلَى ٱلسُّجُودِ فَلَا يَسۡتَطِيعُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5313,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　アッラー*が「その脛を露わにされる」という文字通りに解釈と、その日の「厳しさと恐怖」を表す言い回しである、という説がある（イブン・カスィール８：１９８－１９９参照）。 ２　その日、信仰者はサジダ*できるが、現地で人目や外聞（がいぶん）ゆえにサジダ*していた者は、そうすることが出来ない（アル＝ブハーリー４９１９参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma yuk'shafu ʿan sāqin wayud'ʿawna ilā al-sujūdi falā yastaṭīʿūna ","translations":["(The) Day","will be uncovered","from","the shin","and they will be called","to","prostrate","but not","they will be able","(42)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","yuk'shafu","ʿan","sāqin","wayud'ʿawna","ilā","al-sujūdi","falā","yastaṭīʿūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,1370],[3,1370,1950],[4,1950,3710],[5,3710,4810],[6,4810,5190],[7,5190,6220],[8,6220,6750],[9,6750,10415]]}},{"name":"68:43","price":"怖気づいた目をし、屈辱が彼らを覆う。彼らは確かに（現世で、健康も力も備わっていた）無事な時、サジダ*へと呼ばれていた¹（が、高慢にもそうしなかった）のである。","arabic":"خَٰشِعَةً أَبۡصَٰرُهُمۡ تَرۡهَقُهُمۡ ذِلَّةٞۖ وَقَدۡ كَانُواْ يُدۡعَوۡنَ إِلَى ٱلسُّجُودِ وَهُمۡ سَٰلِمُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5314,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　つまり礼拝や、アッラー*への崇拝*へと呼ばれていた（ムヤッサル５６６頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"khāshiʿatan abṣāruhum tarhaquhum dhillatun waqad kānū yud'ʿawna ilā al-sujūdi wahum sālimūna ","translations":["Humbled","their eyes","will cover them","humiliation","And indeed","they were","called","to","prostrate","while they","(were) sound","(43)"],"transliterationArr":["khāshiʿatan","abṣāruhum","tarhaquhum","dhillatun","waqad","kānū","yud'ʿawna","ilā","al-sujūdi","wahum","sālimūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1270],[2,1270,2660],[3,2660,3850],[4,3850,5190],[5,5190,5750],[6,5750,6540],[7,6540,7470],[8,7470,7860],[9,7860,8890],[10,8890,9400],[11,9400,12765]]}},{"name":"68:44","price":"ならば（使徒*よ）、（クルアーン*の）この話を噓呼ばわりする者を、われに（任せて）放っておけ。われら*は彼らを、彼らが知らない所から徐々に（破滅へと）導いて行こう。¹","arabic":"فَذَرۡنِي وَمَن يُكَذِّبُ بِهَٰذَا ٱلۡحَدِيثِۖ سَنَسۡتَدۡرِجُهُم مِّنۡ حَيۡثُ لَا يَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5315,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　「知らない所から徐々に導いて行く」ことの具体的例については、家畜章４４を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fadharnī waman yukadhibu bihādhā al-ḥadīthi sanastadrijuhum min ḥaythu lā yaʿlamūna ","translations":["So leave Me","and whoever","denies","this","Statement","We will progressively lead them","from","where","not","they know","(44)"],"transliterationArr":["fadharnī","waman","yukadhibu","bihādhā","al-ḥadīthi","sanastadrijuhum","min","ḥaythu","lā","yaʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,930],[2,930,1400],[3,1400,3240],[4,3240,3930],[5,3930,6880],[6,6880,8490],[7,8490,9640],[8,9640,10230],[9,10230,10670],[10,10670,13795]]}},{"name":"68:45","price":"そしてわれら*は彼らに、猶予を与えておくのだ。本当にわが策略¹は、手堅いのだから。","arabic":"وَأُمۡلِي لَهُمۡۚ إِنَّ كَيۡدِي مَتِينٌ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5316,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　彼らに猶予を与えておくことにおける、アッラー*の「策略」については、イムラーン家章１７８を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-um'lī lahum inna kaydī matīnun ","translations":["And I will give respite","to them","Indeed","My plan","(is) firm","(45)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-um'lī","lahum","inna","kaydī","matīnun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,1650],[3,1650,3230],[4,3230,4040],[5,4040,6765]]}},{"name":"68:46","price":"いや（、使徒*よ）、あなたが彼らに見返りを要求し¹、それで彼らは負債ゆえの重荷を背負わされ（、あなたの呼びかけを拒否す）る者だというのか？","arabic":"أَمۡ تَسۡـَٔلُهُمۡ أَجۡرٗا فَهُم مِّن مَّغۡرَمٖ مُّثۡقَلُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5317,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この「見返りの要求」については、家畜章９０の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"am tasaluhum ajran fahum min maghramin muth'qalūna ","translations":["Or","you ask them","a payment","so they","from","(the) debt","(are) burdened","(46)"],"transliterationArr":["am","tasaluhum","ajran","fahum","min","maghramin","muth'qalūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,380],[2,380,1500],[3,1500,2920],[4,2920,3500],[5,3500,4580],[6,4580,6050],[7,6050,10015]]}},{"name":"68:47","price":"それとも、彼らのもとには不可視の世界*（の知識）があり¹、それで彼らが（そこから、人々のために）書き記している²とでも？","arabic":"أَمۡ عِندَهُمُ ٱلۡغَيۡبُ فَهُمۡ يَكۡتُبُونَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5318,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この背景にあることについては、山章４１の訳注を参照。 ２　「書き記している」については、山章４１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"am ʿindahumu al-ghaybu fahum yaktubūna ","translations":["Or","(is) with them","the unseen","so they","write it","(47)"],"transliterationArr":["am","ʿindahumu","al-ghaybu","fahum","yaktubūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,380],[2,380,2150],[3,2150,2990],[4,2990,3620],[5,3620,6675]]}},{"name":"68:48","price":"ならば（使徒*よ）、あなたの主*のお決めになったことゆえに、忍耐*せよ。そして（悲しみで）意気消沈し、（自分の民への懲罰が早く下ることを）祈った時の、大魚の人（預言者*ユーヌス*）のようになるのではない¹。","arabic":"فَٱصۡبِرۡ لِحُكۡمِ رَبِّكَ وَلَا تَكُن كَصَاحِبِ ٱلۡحُوتِ إِذۡ نَادَىٰ وَهُوَ مَكۡظُومٞ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5319,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　ユーヌス*が「大魚の人」と呼ばれる由来については、預言者*たち章８７「ズン＝ヌーン」 の訳注を参照。また、この話の背景にある出来事については、同章とその訳注、及び整列者章１３９－１４８を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-iṣ'bir liḥuk'mi rabbika walā takun kaṣāḥibi al-ḥūti idh nādā wahuwa makẓūmun ","translations":["So be patient","for (the) decision","(of) your Lord","and (do) not","be","like (the) companion","(of) the fish","when","he called out","while he","(was) distressed","(48)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-iṣ'bir","liḥuk'mi","rabbika","walā","takun","kaṣāḥibi","al-ḥūti","idh","nādā","wahuwa","makẓūmun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,740],[2,740,1540],[3,1540,2350],[4,2350,2840],[5,2840,4000],[6,4000,5040],[7,5040,5840],[8,5840,6150],[9,6150,6990],[10,6990,7510],[11,7510,10695]]}},{"name":"68:49","price":"もし、（彼の悔悟が受け入れられることにより¹、）彼の主*からのご慈悲が彼に降りかからなければ、彼は謗られつつ、不毛の地に放り去られたであろう。","arabic":"لَّوۡلَآ أَن تَدَٰرَكَهُۥ نِعۡمَةٞ مِّن رَّبِّهِۦ لَنُبِذَ بِٱلۡعَرَآءِ وَهُوَ مَذۡمُومٞ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5320,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この時の様子と悔悟の言葉については、預言者たち章８７を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"lawlā an tadārakahu niʿ'matun min rabbihi lanubidha bil-ʿarāi wahuwa madhmūmun ","translations":["If not","that","overtook him","a Favor","from","his Lord","surely he would have been thrown","onto (the) naked shore","while he","(was) blamed","(49)"],"transliterationArr":["lawlā","an","tadārakahu","niʿ'matun","min","rabbihi","lanubidha","bil-ʿarāi","wahuwa","madhmūmun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2280],[2,2280,3280],[3,3280,4700],[4,4700,5550],[5,5550,6460],[6,6460,7700],[7,7700,8430],[8,8430,11380],[9,11380,11900],[10,11900,14465]]}},{"name":"68:50","price":"だが、かれの主*は彼を選び抜かれ、彼を正しい者*たちの一人とされた。","arabic":"فَٱجۡتَبَٰهُ رَبُّهُۥ فَجَعَلَهُۥ مِنَ ٱلصَّٰلِحِينَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5321,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-ij'tabāhu rabbuhu fajaʿalahu mina al-ṣāliḥīna ","translations":["But chose him","his Lord","and made him","of","the righteous","(50)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-ij'tabāhu","rabbuhu","fajaʿalahu","mina","al-ṣāliḥīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1270],[2,1270,2160],[3,2160,3370],[4,3370,3740],[5,3740,7365]]}},{"name":"68:51","price":"（使徒*よ、）不信仰に陥った者*たちは教訓（クルアーン*）を耳にした時、その視線によって、あなたを今にも躓かせんばかりである¹。そして彼らは、言うのだ。「本当に彼（ムハンマド*）は、まさに憑かれた者²である」。","arabic":"وَإِن يَكَادُ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ لَيُزۡلِقُونَكَ بِأَبۡصَٰرِهِمۡ لَمَّا سَمِعُواْ ٱلذِّكۡرَ وَيَقُولُونَ إِنَّهُۥ لَمَجۡنُونٞ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5322,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　つまり、「アイン（邪視）を及ぼす」という意味（ムヤッサル５６６頁参照）。ほかにも「滅ぼす」「視線で射抜く」「（アッラー*から授かった地位から）退（しりぞ）かせる」「（イスラーム*の教えを伝達するという任務から）逸らせる」というような解釈があるが、アル＝クルトゥビー*によれば、これら全ての説は「アインを及ぼす」という意味から派生したもの（１８：２５５－２５６参照）。尚「アイン」とは、悪い性質を帯びた者から発される、嫉妬（しっと）が混じった羨望（せんぼう）の視線のことで、それによって視線の対象が害を被（こうむ）る類いのもの（クウェイト法学大全３１：１１９－１２０参照）。 ２　「憑かれた者」については、アル＝ヒジュル章６の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-in yakādu alladhīna kafarū layuz'liqūnaka bi-abṣārihim lammā samiʿū al-dhik'ra wayaqūlūna innahu lamajnūnun ","translations":["And indeed","would almost","those who","disbelieve","surely make you slip","with their look","when","they hear","the Message","and they say","Indeed, he","(is) surely mad","(51)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-in","yakādu","alladhīna","kafarū","layuz'liqūnaka","bi-abṣārihim","lammā","samiʿū","al-dhik'ra","wayaqūlūna","innahu","lamajnūnun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1150],[2,1150,1890],[3,1890,2850],[4,2850,3710],[5,3710,5370],[6,5370,6970],[7,6970,8200],[8,8200,8870],[9,8870,9690],[10,9690,11000],[11,11000,12500],[12,12500,15915]]}},{"name":"68:52","price":"それは全世界への教訓に、外ならないというのに。","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ إِلَّا ذِكۡرٞ لِّلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["68 (Al-Qalam)","Al-Qalam","Surah Al-Qalam"],"ayahNumber":5323,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā huwa illā dhik'run lil'ʿālamīna ","translations":["And not","it (is)","but","a Reminder","to the worlds","(52)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","huwa","illā","dhik'run","lil'ʿālamīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1010],[3,1010,1930],[4,1930,2570],[5,2570,8175]]}}],